{"tid":572220,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過成功等到自己鍾意既人?","createTime":"2018-02-25T11:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T18:50:19.000Z","uid":58333,"like":41,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d9bcd61592ef9ba48b57459c057471308730e25c","tid":572220,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴絲<br />\n唔知大家有無試過鍾意左個拍緊拖既人<br />\n唯有一直等 唔插手唔做第三者 拒絕晒其他追自己既人 一尾係到等<br />\n而之後佢地又真係散左<br />\n而最後自己就同果位對象一齊左?<br />\n分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1af6df309ad35de137c307d2cc4df8a4c417bf4","tid":572220,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":50,"score":-46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cda30f99fd7ef5b12eecb579f4f2ef02418b3e77","tid":572220,"uid":124170,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人少啲性幻想啦"},{"pid":"8bf0e8825087c0fd587e723f7ca98be53036f811","tid":572220,"uid":58333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cda30f99fd7ef5b12eecb579f4f2ef02418b3e77","tid":572220,"uid":124170,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人少啲性幻想啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"我都覺得呢類經驗太唔真實<br />\n所以先想知有無人真係試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1029694760ed8cc6c543c31c420f46f381555f88","tid":572220,"uid":102096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4859481d899c308e334b9712cbf24936eb4f1419","tid":572220,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cda30f99fd7ef5b12eecb579f4f2ef02418b3e77","tid":572220,"uid":124170,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人少啲性幻想啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"AGGER"},{"pid":"8793eeb8079a190b5326d3bf74a7b182b1cc6c24","tid":572220,"uid":165482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"你做第一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8452d3911ee6d5fe66e1a28d9f291e5f63a86ede","tid":572220,"uid":126651,"like":23,"dislike":85,"score":-62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家個未婚夫<br />\n個陣因爲佔中所以識到佢<br />\n話說當年我同ex一齊左四年<br />\n因為傾結婚 我壓力大到有抑鬱<br />\n最後明白對方都唔係岩個個<br />\n所以決定分開<br />\n到我同我ex散左後 <br />\n我斷晒當時識嘅所有男性朋友嘅聯絡<br />\n因為唔想聽同見到任何異性<br />\n佢冇停過搵我<br />\n我試過有次我係公園喊(掛住ex)<br />\n佢咁岩路過 見到我<br />\n我個陣發晒癲咁鬧爆佢<br />\n真係指住個頭咁鬧 <br />\n叫佢走 唔好再煩我 <br />\n佢第二日朝早whatsapp我<br />\n「今日心情有冇好d？」<br />\n我真係打左個突<br />\n佢每日都會sd幾個wts比我<br />\n我通常都係hea覆或者唔覆<br />\n後來我同左第二個一齊<br />\n佢依舊每日都sd幾個wts黎<br />\n我真係覺得佢痴L線<br />\n:<br />\n我同第二個個男仔一齊左<br />\n好快就散左<br />\n佢個陣唔知我散左<br />\n佢話唔介意我有男朋友 話佢係我背後後盾<br />\n但我冇點理過佢<br />\n:<br />\n但去到最後，真係比佢感動到<br />\n佢就係咁愛我、包容我、愛護我<br />\n陪我一齊成長<br />\n我本來好驚結婚 (始終上一次算係衰左)<br />\n係佢陪我走出陰影<br />\n令我感到幸福<br />\n:<br />\n真係要多謝佢當年等左我咁耐<br />\n我會用我地嘅將來證明<br />\n你嘅等待係值得嘅<br />\n❤️"},{"pid":"fab07fc9d33ccda4a01b496c87df8c7aaead0c85","tid":572220,"uid":70496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f71c6e9a8d8b73cacf761091a461d275d46bbed","tid":572220,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"其實唔難"},{"pid":"e8682b094531325459c6f074b9d8bd29ab65dac9","tid":572220,"uid":828,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/25/201912_816f6180a314f66ce0a7b1c048ec15e0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F25%2F201912_816f6180a314f66ce0a7b1c048ec15e0.jpeg&h=1356f018&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38492d197e75fd43f1d2377756a12d